  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Survival beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.4tTkRyOQ0VuRBac3]{Terrain Expertise}</li><li>When expert: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.BV5jpSifVJsTwoO7]{Wilderness Spotter}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.dbLMuzTrci1l3X0X]{Resilience Path - Trained}</strong>: Your body is especially resilient against hardships.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.kOWJkYnuwvYaAbMn]{Foraging Path - Trained}</strong>: You are a master at procuring rations in dire situations.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.oUPFbBi1zruenReB]{Wayfinding Path - Trained}</strong>: Your ability to orientate yourself is unparalleled.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.akDMA5is25MRAVpO]{Preparedness Path - Trained}</strong>: You have the almost uncanny ability to predict difficult situations and prepare for them.</li></ul>",
      "gm": ""
    },
